<speaker>용준</speaker>
<p>뭘 불어?</p>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>정금</speaker>
<p>누구랑 전화했어?</p>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>용준</speaker>
<p>빨리 자 그냥..</p>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>정금</speaker>
